都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dc375c8989b6fd563ab9123d67d2dcc1b658d10e","tid":1544774,"uid":12007,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"09f377a1aa6b093b40d578130445ad0d413058e0","tid":1544774,"uid":292497,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:21:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屯門和平到仆街<br />\n利申屯門友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:21:41.000Z","msg":"咪係囉，咁和平跳閘都無人做"},{"pid":"5dc0c1da9cc739e5995b52c62ec05945d1a86b87","tid":1544774,"uid":309888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:22:05.000Z","msg":"河田嗰邊跳 易突破心理關口啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc5e40abe7d662ce01de0e63a03a72da521ec0a0","tid":1544774,"uid":266336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:22:50.000Z","msg":"